node.text:
🎀跟住心情配搭頭箍上嘅毛公仔裝飾，隨時換款式又得，鍾意點自拍都得📸！

🎀 Sparkle up your day your way with the perfect customizable headband to match your mood. Then grab a silly happy selfie 📸!

#香港迪士尼樂園 #HKDisneyland #放開心更開心 #GetSillyHappy #HappierHere

The curious little fox 🦊 LinaBell will be joining Duffy & Friends and embarking on a series of adventures 🦋!
 
充滿好奇心嘅小狐狸LinaBell即將登場🦊，期待與Duffy & Friends展開連串有趣冒險故事🦋！
 
#DuffyAndFriends #LinaBell  #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

Gather 'round📢 It's time for a springtime adventure🌸! Join Duffy and friends to welcome the arrival of spring🌷🌻🌿集合📢開展春日奇妙之旅🌸！快啲加入Duffy同佢班好朋友，一齊探索大自然，迎接春天嘅來臨🌷🌻🌿#DuffyAndFriends #香港迪士尼樂園 #HKDisneyland

Joy from Inside Out is always brimming with optimism! Let's draw a portrait of her ✍️ to start the new year with positive vibes🤗阿樂充滿正能量，能夠抱著樂觀嘅態度面對未來。不如喺新嘅一年，我哋攞起畫筆畫吓阿樂✍️，為自己注入更多開心嘅力量🤗#MagicAtHome #Joy #InsideOut #AnimationAcademy #HKDisneyland #阿樂 #玩轉腦朋友 #香港迪士尼樂園

Want to recreate Elsa and her magical powers? ❄️❄️ Pick up a pencil and learn to illustrate her bravery and courage. 👑 
喺冬天有冇諗起愛莎同佢嘅冰雪魔法？❄️❄️而家就攞起畫筆，畫畫女王愛莎👑，感受佢勇敢向前嘅力量💫

#MagicAtHome #Frozen #Elsa #AnimationAcademy #HKDisneyland #魔雪奇緣 #愛莎 #動畫藝術教室 #香港迪士尼樂園

Disney friends miss you so much👋Come see what magic that awaits you⭐️
迪士尼朋友好掛住你👋為咗歡迎你嘅蒞臨，你估米奇同佢班朋友點樣準備？一齊睇睇啦🧐

#BelieveInMagic #GetReadyWithMickey #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

We've all heard of Simba's story📚: We are all connected in the great Circle of Life. Be like Simba, and believe in yourself when facing challenges❣️Now, let's pick up a pencil and channel Simba's incredible courage👊👊
辛巴嘅成長故事話畀我哋聽📚： 每個人喺生命循環當中都有自己嘅位置。面對逆境，記住好似辛巴一樣，積極面對❣️而家就攞起畫筆，畫出辛巴嘅無比嘅勇氣啦👊👊

#MagicAtHome #AnimationAcademy #LionKing #HKDisneyland #獅子王 #香港迪士尼樂園

Your pen is your magic wand! 🖌This time, let's learn how to draw Sorcerer Mickey! Get ready, class is in session!
你嘅筆就係魔法棒🖌，今次有請迪士尼動畫師教我哋點畫魔法師米奇。準備，課堂開始！

#MagicAtHome #AnimationAcademy #SorcererMickey #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

Want to learn how to draw Minnie? 👩🎨Let our Disney Animator show you how!
想畫出甜美動人嘅米妮？👩🎨等迪士尼動畫師教你當中嘅秘訣！
⠀⠀
#MinnieMouse #AnimationAcademy #動畫藝術教室 #香港迪士尼樂園 #HKDisneyland

Pick up a pen and join our Disney Animation Academy Artist for a lesson on drawing the adorable Tinker Bell🧚at home!
一齊在家跟迪士尼動畫師揮揮畫筆，可愛嘅🧚‍♀️Tinker Bell即將誕生喇！
⠀⠀
#畫出無限想像 #動畫藝術教室 #AnimationAcademy #TinkerBell #香港迪士尼樂園 #HKDisneyland

究竟米奇會點準備聖誕🎄？等唐老鴨帶你直擊啦👀！
⠀⠀
#奇妙聖誕 #讓歡樂相傳 #TreasureYourTraditions #ADisneyChristmas #DisneyChristmas #香港迪士尼樂園 #HKDisneyland

🍂深秋涼風輕輕掠過城堡，最啱嚟樂園探索更多奇妙樂趣🏰！
 
🍂When the soft sun shines on the Castle of Magical Dreams, and you can feel the crisp air calling, it’s time to take a visit and enjoy magical fall fun🏰! 

#HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🍬快啲嚟樂園搵出唔同造型嘅南瓜頭趣玩站，一齊Trick-or-Treat啦！

🍬Trick-or-treat around the park and discover all our wacky jack-o'-lanterns.

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🧡米奇同成班迪士尼朋友LinaBell喺大街上載歌載舞歡慶萬聖節🔔！

🧡Mickey and friends come and dance at Mickey's Halloween Time Street Party🔔 

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

👠灰姑娘嘅邪惡後母杜明尼夫人帶埋兩個女安蒂、狄茜，齊齊露出「憎」面目🖤！ 

👠Lady Tremaine from 'Cinderella' and her two daughters, Anastasia and Drizella, make their first evil appearance in the park🖤！

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🎨畫上迪士尼萬聖彩繪，為派對造型更添繽紛詭趣🖌️。

🎨Jazz up your spooky Halloween style with creative body paint🖌️.

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🎶「惡」滿全城，精彩嘅「惡人舞動迪士尼」梗係要一睇再睇🎹！

🎶 Let's get wild, and Let's Get Wicked! Don't stop till you get enough🎹！

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🍿你食咗充滿邪惡滋味嘅爆谷未呀?！

🍿Have you tried our popcorn with an evil touch? 🍩

 #惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🏰展開「迪士尼星夢光影之旅」，再「驚」歷一次惡人嘅考驗✨！

🏰 Join the "Momentous" journey and experience spooky times with the Disney Villains.✨！

#惡晒出黎 #反轉#迪士尼 #DisneyFriends #Disneygram #DisneyLove #DisneyIG #InstaDisney #InstaDaily #PhotooftheDay #hkig #HongKong #香港 #discoverhongkong #香港好去處 #hkg

🎃南瓜王阿Jack設宴，讓你品嘗最地道嘅怪誕城「瘋」味🥂！

🎃 You're invited to Jack the Pumpkin King’s dinner to have a taste of evil🥂!

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🪩邪惡魅力四射嘅庫伊拉，喺佢嘅專屬舞台等梗你嚟狂歡熱舞🎙️！

🪩The wickedly dazzling Cruella is waiting for you to rock her stage🎙️！

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🛍️想擁有烏蘇拉一頭標誌性白髮，就要嚟樂園選購最新嘅發光頭箍啦💡！

🛍️Do you want to have Ursula’s signature white hair? Get a glowing headband to create your favorite Disney Villain look!

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園

🎶萬聖節惡門大開，烏蘇拉都要從深海洞穴嚟到原野劇場一展渾厚魔性嘅歌喉。

🎶 To celebrate the spookiest time of year, Ursula will rise from her home in the remains of a leviathan to reveal to the world her deep and mesmerizing voice.

#惡晒出黎 #反轉迪士尼 #ShowYourWickedSide #DisneyHalloweenTime #Halloween #DisneyVillains #HKDisneyland #香港迪士尼樂園
